# Puchi Infrastructure

Infrastructure as Code — ArgoCD GitOps trên K3s 3-node HA.

## Cluster

| Node | IP | Role |
|------|-----|------|
| k3s-node1 | 192.168.100.201 | control-plane, etcd |
| k3s-node2 | 192.168.100.202 | control-plane, etcd |
| k3s-node3 | 192.168.100.203 | control-plane, etcd |

K3s v1.35.5, storage: `local-path`, ingress: Traefik.

## Cấu trúc repo

```
puchi-infra/
├── argocd/
│   ├── projects/infra.yaml         # AppProject: puchi
│   └── apps/
│       ├── root.yaml               # App of Apps root
│       ├── repo-creds.yaml         # GitHub credentials
│       ├── puchi-db.yaml           # PostgreSQL cluster
│       ├── envoy-gateway-routes.yaml  # Envoy Gateway config
│       ├── puchi-frontend.yaml     # Frontend deployment
│       └── puchi-backend.yaml     # 5 backend services
├── infra/
│   ├── postgres-cluster/           # CloudNativePG CRDs
│   ├── envoy-gateway/              # Envoy Gateway config
│   ├── frontend/web/               # Frontend K8s manifests
│   └── backend/                    # 5 backend service manifests
│       ├── auth/                   # Auth-service (Limen)
│       ├── core/                   # Profile, onboarding, social
│       ├── learn/
│       ├── media/
│       └── notification/           # Gotify + Tino SMTP (email.send)
├── scripts/
│   ├── bootstrap.sh                # ArgoCD bootstrap
│   ├── setup-r2.sh                 # R2 bucket + media secret
│   ├── setup-smtp.sh               # Tino SMTP → notification-smtp secret
│   └── setup-nats.sh               # NATS streams
└── README.md
```

## Services dùng chung với Arda

| Service | Namespace | Mô tả |
|---------|-----------|-------|
| CloudNativePG | cnpg-system | PostgreSQL operator |
| NATS | platform | Message broker, prefix `puchi.*` / subjects `email.send`, `learn.*` |
| Valkey (Redis) | platform | Cache, DB index riêng |
| Traefik | kube-system | Ingress controller |
| ArgoCD | argocd | GitOps deploy |
| Cloudflare Tunnel | platform | Expose ra internet |

Object storage Puchi: **Cloudflare R2** (`puchi-media`, CDN `cdn.puchi.io.vn`) — không dùng Garage cho media.

